** that:\\n1. **Captures data at two points**: prompt start + commit time\\n2. **Tracks per-file user additions** for accurate ownership estimation\\n3. **Uses LIFO heuristic** for line-level approximation without complexity\\n4. **Stores in checkpoint metadata** (JSON on `entire/checkpoints/v1` branch)\\n5. **Avoids overkill solutions** (git blame, line hashing, position tracking)\\n6. **Accepts trade-offs** (medium accuracy vs. low complexity)\\n\\nThe system is **informational, not security-critical**, and the per-file pool approach handles the common case (users editing their own recent code) well.\"}],\"totalDurationMs\":47363,\"totalTokens\":101943,\"totalToolUseCount\":21,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":8330,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":91295,\"output_tokens\":2315,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":8330},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"687a5c41-dd7e-474b-a481-3e8c09b76d78\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"d6583738-afa1-477a-b0b4-bac272f162a7\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"09356618-966a-4751-9a19-8254300ef35a\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"slug\":\"linked-chasing-storm\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01RFsfZLt2apZC3kuHGenvif\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Excellent research. Now let me read the key architecture doc and attribution code to get precise details for the playground.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":2736,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":31811,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":2736},\"output_tokens\":3,\"service_tier\":\"sta