emovals target agent code (unfairly penalizing the agent). The per-file pool heuristic instead assumes users modify their own recent additions first: `selfMod = min(removals, userPriorAdds)` per file. This preserves agent credit when users refactor their own code.\\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\\n\\n### Playground features:\\n\\n- **5 scenarios** in the sidebar (keys 1-5): Agent Only, Mixed, Heavy Editing, Self-Modification, Multi-File\\n- **Step through the timeline** with arrow keys or clicking steps to see code evolve\\n- **Code View** — color-coded lines (blue=human, green=agent) with the full calculation breakdown\\n- **Git Trees** tab — visualizes the three-tree model and diffs between them\\n- **LIFO Demo** tab — click lines to \\\"remove\\\" them and compare with/without per-file tracking\\n\\nTry the **Self-Modification** preset (key 4) — it best demonstrates why LIFO matters (66.7% vs incorrect 46.7%).\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":119,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":112800,\"output_tokens\":482,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":119,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYnG9VwGVFtDmNdcMHGw5\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"64fc6c3b-00a5-47d8-aa9b-b59e4f5e261d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T17:59:47.725Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"64fc6c3b-00a5-47d8-aa9b-b59e4f5e261d\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"09356618-966a-4751-9a19-8254300ef35a\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"slug\":\"linked-chasing-storm\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go